so%20little%20relationship%20history%20or%20maybe%20because%20of%20my%20own%20wiring%2C%20I%20needed%20to%20work%20toward%20forgiveness%20in%20the%20same%20relationship%20where%20I%20had%20been%20hurt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don't%20do%20well%20with%20unanswered%20questions%2C%20and%20this%20kind%20of%20betrayal%20left%20a%20lot%20of%20them.%20I%20also%20needed%20to%20understand%20my%20partner's%20traumas%20and%20history%20to%20understand%20why%20this%20pattern%20of%20cheating%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20predated%20me%20by%20at%20least%2020%20years%20and%20had%20persisted%20throughout%20all%20of%20their%20relationships%20%E2%80%94%20existed%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20I%20needed%20to%20know%20where%20I%20had%20failed%20myself%2C%20where%20I%20had%20not%20realized%20the%20ways%20I%20was%20being%20taken%20advantage%20of%2C%20where%20I%20had%20not%20remained%20true%20to%20the%20person%20I%20am%20and%20want%20to%20be%20by%20allowing%20someone%20to%20lie%20to%20me%20even%20when%20I%20didn't%20yet%20have%20proof%20that%20they%20were%2C%20besides%20the%20feeling%20inside%20the%20pit%20of%20my%20stomach.%20So%2C%20I%20stayed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226aa8fa2e-cd9f-403c-8242-618acae3a218%5C%22%3EI%20needed%20to%20forgive%20myself%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20months%20that%20followed%20were%2C%20at%20times%2C%20exhilarating%20and%2C%20at%20times%2C%20excruciating.%20I%20went%20through%20all%20the%20typical%20patterns%20of%20someone%20who%20has%20been%20cheated%20on%3A%20I%20wanted%20to%20control%20my%20partner's%20actions%2C%20where%20they%20went%2C%20and%20who%20they%20spoke%20to.%20Their%20phone%20was%20a%20major%20source%20of%20anxiety%20and%20a%20trigger%20for%20me.%20We%20had%20exhausting%20fights%2C%20and%20I%20doubted%20my%20decision%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThings%20changed%20when%20I%20began%20to%20reframe%20the%20goal%20of%20forgiveness%20as%20exclusively%20something%20for%20me%20to%20give%20myself.%20For%20too%20long%2C%20forgiveness%20was%20sought%20after%20by%20both%20my%20partner%20and%20me%20as%20a%20kind%20of%20way%20to%20redeem%20them%20%E2%80%94%20once%20I%20realized%20that%20forgiveness%20was%20internal%2C%20that%20allowing%20myself%20to%20be%20soft%20and%20understand%20that%20trusting%20someone%20I%20loved%20wasn't%20something%20I%20did%20wrong%2C%20my%20heart%20began%20to%20open%20to%20other%20ways%20forgiveness%20could%20be%20extended%20to%20my%20partner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20a%20strong%20connection%20to%20myself%20these%20days%2C%20and%20it's%20something%20that%20has%20carried%20me%20even%20when%20small%20arguments%20pop%20off%20or%20something%20reminds%20me%20of%20what%20happened.%20Triggers%20are%20significantly%20more%20rare.%20I%20realized%20through%20this%20process%20that%20at%20my%20most%20fundamental%20level%2C%20I%20am%20someone%20who%20believes%20in%20redemption%20%E2%80%94%20crucially%2C%20I'd%20like%20to%20note%2C%20only%20once%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20isn't%20something%20that%20I%20want%20to%20lose.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20now%20in%20this%20relationship%20with%20my%20eyes%20wide%20open%20and%20knowing%20what%20my%20partner%20is%20capable%20of%2C%20and%20if%20the%20same%20red%20flags%20show%20up%2C%20if%20something%20doesn't%20feel%20right%20again%2C%20I%20could%20now%20walk%20away%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20am%20choosing%20to%20trust%2C%20and%20choosing%20to%20stay%20close%20to%20the%20person%20I%20am.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforgiving-partner-who-cheated-actually-meant-forgiving-myself-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727093803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f15366ce3009a0fac85ddc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforgiving-partner-who-cheated-actually-me