%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20calls%20date%20back%20to%20May%202023%20after%20which%2C%20on%20June%2014%2C%20Kunal%20Chhabra%20had%20complained%20to%20the%20police.%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20who%20has%20been%20in%20Gujarat's%20Sabarmati%20jail%2C%20has%20been%20questioned%20by%20the%20police%20but%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20what%20action%20has%20been%20taken.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20audio%20clips%2C%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20is%20heard%20saying%20that%20because%20of%20Kunal%20Chhabra%2C%2010%20of%20his%20men%20have%20been%20arrested.%20%26quot%3BNow%20you%20have%20incurred%20our%20enmity...%20We%20have%20suffered%20a%20lot%20because%20of%20you.%20Now%20our%20own%20people%20will%20take%20care%20of%20you%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20accused%20Kunal%20Chhabra%20of%20paying%20money%20to%20policemen%2C%20because%20of%20which%20the%20arrests%20were%20made.%20%C2%A0Chhabra%20denied%20he%20had%20done%20anything.%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20give%20money%20to%20any%20policemen.%20I%20got%20a%20call%2C%20someone%20from%20your%20STF%20called%20from%20Punjab.%20he%20asked%20me%20that%20I%20got%20a%20call%20and%20why%20have%20I%20not%20complained.%20I%20said%20that%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20complain.%20I%20will%20also%20give%20you%20the%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20is%20heard%20saying.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%20call%2C%20Bishnoi%20is%20heard%20demanding%20Rs%205%20crore%2C%20which%20Chhabra%20promised%20to%20pay%20once%20he%20returned%20to%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKunal%20Chhabra%20had%20defaulted%20on%20the%20payment%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20his%20friend%20Nadir%20Shah%2C%20a%20gym%20owner%20from%20Delhi.%20On%20September%2012%20this%20year%2C%20Nadir%20Shah%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20south%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20from%20a%20nearby%20CCTV%20camera%20in%20Greater%20Kailash-1%20showed%20him%20standing%20and%20talking%20to%20one%20of%20his%20associates%20when%20a%20man%20in%20a%20checked%20sh