dhi's%20stature%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20Monday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20cannot%20be%20a%20(more)%20foolish%20statement%20than%20saying%20'funds%20coming%20from%20the%20Centre%2C%20or%20the%20state's%20funds%20for%20development%2C%20are%20being%20given%20to%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20openly%20challenge%20Kangana%20to%20show%20proof%20of%20even%20Re%201%20being%20diverted...%20or%20apologise%20to%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20for%20such%20baseless%20allegations...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20also%20slammed%20Ms%20Ranaut's%20%26quot%3Bintellectual%20bankruptcy%26quot%3B%2C%20pointing%20out%20the%20actor-politician%20had%2C%20only%20last%20month%2C%20been%20reprimanded%20by%20her%20party%20over%20comments%20about%20the%20farmers'%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20has%20already%20cautioned%20her...%20to%20not%20issue%20a%20statement%20on%20sensitive%20issues.%20However%2C%20it%20seem%20she%20has%20not%20paid%20heed%20to%20the%20advice%20of%20her%20party's%20high%20command%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshes-not-authorised-bjp-on-kangana-ranauts-farmers-protest-remarks-6421584%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBJP%20Schools%20Actor-MP%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20Over%20Farmer%20Remarks%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20specific%20charge%20-%20that%20the%20Congress'%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20government%20%26quot%3Btakes%20loans%20and%20gives%20it%20to%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20which%20has%20made%20the%20state's%20finances%20hollow%26quot%3B%20-%20Mr%20Singh%20pointed%20out%20money%20from%20the%20central%20government%2C%20and%20the%20uses%20to%20which%20it%20is%20put%2C%20are%20properly%20audited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20defamatory%20statement%20and%20we%20condemn%20it.%20She%20should%20produce%20evidence%20in%20a%20week...%20if%20she%20doesn't%2C%20and%20doesn't%20apologise%2C%20we%20will%20file%20a%20criminal%20defamation%20case...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20launching%20a%20membership%20drive%20in%20her%20constituency%2C%20Ms%20Ranaut%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20and%20attacked%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDisasters%20and%20Congress%20have%20taken%20the%20state%20back%20decades...%20I%20appeal%20to%20the%20people%20to%20root%20out%20this%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20(the%20central%20government)%20gives%20disaster%20funds%2C%20it%20should%20go%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Relief%20Fund...%20but%20everyone%20knows%20that%20it%20goes%20to%20the%20'Sonia%20Relief%20Fund'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor-politician%20also%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20-%20her%20rival%20for%20the%20Mandi%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20the%20April-June%20general%20election.%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20are%20tired%20of%20potholes%20on%20roads...%20I%20would%20do%20more%20than%20possible%20for%20my%20area%2C%20but%20the%20PWD%20Minister%20should%20also%20do%20something%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimachal%20Pradesh%20is%20battling%20a%20financial%20crisis%20inflamed%20by%20devastating%20landslides%2C%20flash%20floods%2C%20and%20heavy%20rain%20in%20August%2C%20last%20year%20and%20this.%20To%20combat%20this%20problem%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20last%20month%20said%20his%20cabinet%20colleagues%20and%20he%20would%20defer%20accepting%20salaries%20for%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhimachal-pradesh-chief-minister-sukhvinder-sukhu-defer-salaries-2-months-crisis-hit-himachal-chief-minister-ministers-defer-salaries-for-2-months-6444165%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECrisis-Hit%20Himachal%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Minist