-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20schools%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20said%20are%20both%20high%20quality%20and%20affordable.%20He%20said%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20went%20back%20to%20the%20Netherlands%20for%20a%20few%20months%20for%20the%20birth%20of%20their%20child%20due%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bsubstandard%26quot%3B%20healthcare%20in%20Iraq.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Netherlands'%20biggest%20financial%20downsides%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eare%20that%20rent%2C%20groceries%2C%20public%20transportation%2C%20and%20energy%20costs%20have%20gotten%20more%20expensive%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22915f0aab-0318-4f5d-943f-39098262ff06%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20adventure%20of%20traveling%20the%20world%20has%20been%20worthwhile%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chris%20Oberman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e9969dd17aa3c7b2b34f51%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChris%20Oberman%20said%20he%20sometimes%20misses%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20but%20that%20he%20loves%20the%20%26quot%3Badventures%26quot%3B%20that%20come%20with%20living%20internationally.%20%3Cp%3EChris%20Oberman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20any%20financial%20challenge%2C%20Oberman%20said%20the%20toughest%20part%20about%20living%20internationally%20has%20been%20being%20away%20from%20friends%20and%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20I'm%20back%20home%2C%20the%20stories%20I%20tell%20don't%20quite%20resonate%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20being%20able%20to%20really%20share%20those%20adventures%20is%20something%20I%20didn't%20expect%20would%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20doesn't%20regret%20the%20path%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20have%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20chose%20this%20life%20because%20we%20love%20to%20