.%20Indeed%2C%20this%20summit%20has%20been%20successful%20in%20signalling%20-%20'The%20Quad%20is%20here%20to%20stay'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20of%20highly%20complex%20global%20crises%20playing%20out%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20Quad%20leaders'%20summit%20took%20place%20in%20the%20context%20of%20critical%20challenges%20and%20vital%20opportunities.%20With%20enduring%20wars%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20China's%20belligerent%20activities%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%20and%20emerging%20non-traditional%20security%20challenges%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20Quad%20had%20its%20task%20cut%20out.%20The%20Wilmington%20Declaration%20-%20the%20joint%20statement%20of%20the%20Quad%20leaders%20-%20amply%20addressed%20these%20critical%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Wilmington%20Statement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Quad%20grouping%20in%20Wilmington%20exhibits%20continuity%20in%20responding%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20reiterating%20the%20urgent%20need%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20conflict%20and%20uphold%20the%20spirit%20of%20international%20law.%20Similarly%2C%20this%20year's%20statement%20expressed%20concerns%20over%20ballistic%20missile%20launches%20conducted%20by%20North%20Korea%20and%20the%20need%20to%20prevent%20the%20proliferation%20of%20nuclear%20missiles%20and%20technologies.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20Wilmington%20Declaration%20focused%20on%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20shared%20its%20concerns%20over%20the%20ongoing%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20Gaza%20advocating%20for%20a%20sovereign%2C%20viable%2C%20and%20independent%20state%20of%20Palestine%20while%20remaining%20sensitive%20to%20the%20concerns%20of%20Israel.%20Apart%20from%20these%2C%20the%20statement%20further%20reiterated%20concerns%20over%20the%20worsening%20political%20and%20humanitarian%20situation%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20as%20well%20as%20attacks%20by%20the%20Houthis%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20Gulf%20of%20Aden.%3Cbr%3E%5CnHowever%2C%20China%20remained%20the%20big-ticket%20question%20for%20the%20Quad%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20context.%20On%20the%20China%20question%2C%20Quad's%20response%20this%20year%20seems%20sharper%20than%20the%20previous%20years.%20Earlier%2C%20at%20the%20Quad%20Foreign%20Ministers'%20meet%2C%20the%20grouping%20called%20Beijing%20out%20-%20albeit%20without%20naming%20it%20-%20for%20disregarding%20international%20law%20and%20unilaterally%20acting%20in%20the%20East%20and%20South%20China%20Sea%20region.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20Quad%20leaders%20expressed%20their%20concern%20over%20increasing%20militarisation%20in%20disputed%20pockets%20of%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%20Responding%20to%20the%20tensions%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20grouping%20condemned%20the%20use%20of%20coastguards%20and%20maritime%20militia%20vessels%2C%20which%20serve%20as%20China's%20tactics%20for%20coercive%20and%20intimidating%20manoeuvres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Slew%20Of%20Announcements%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuad's%20synergy%20on%20issues%20of%20maritime%20safety%20and%20security%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20has%20also%20gained%20vital%20momentum%20at%20this%20summit.%20A%20joint%20coastguard-level%20cooperation%20among%20the%20four%20Quad%20countries%20-%20Quad-at-Sea%20Ship%20Observer%20Mission%20-%20proposed%20at%20the%20summit%20seeks%20to%20improve%20interoperability%20among%20the%20coastguard%20services%20of%20the%20four%20countries%2C%20advancing%20cooperation%20in%20the%20domain%20of%20maritime%20safety%20and%20security.%20Similarly%2C%20responding%20to%20the%20imminent%20challenges%20posed%20by%20natural%20calamities%20and%20disasters%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20the%20grouping%20announced%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20'Quad%20Indo-Pacific%20Logistics%20Network'%2C%20which%20is%20meant%20to%20pursue%20shared%20airlift%20capacities%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20improve%20cooperation%20in%20the%20domain%20of%20Humanitarian%20Assistance%20and%20Disaster%20Relief%20(HADR)%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Quad's%20efforts%20to%20bolster%20Maritime%20Domain%20Awareness%20through%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20Partnership%20for%20Maritime%20Domain%20Awareness%20(IPMDA)%20received%20a%20significant%20push%20with%20Australia%20committing%20to%20involve%20the%20Pacific%20Islands%20Forum%20Fisheries%20Agency%20to%20enhance%20cooperation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20by%20the%20grouping%20proposing%20a%20new%20Maritime%20Initiative%20for%20Training%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20(MAITRI).%20This%20summit%20further%20consolidated%20its%20regional%20partnerships%20through%20continued%20cooperation%20with%20the%20Association%20of%20Southeast%20Asian%20Nations%20(ASEAN)%2C%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Rim%20Association%20(IORA)%2C%20and%20the%20Pacific%20Islands%20Forum%20(PIF).%20Notably%2C%20the%20Quad%20Fellowship%20programme%20has%20been%20expanded%20to%20include%20students%20from%20ASEAN%20countries%20demonstrating%20the%20grouping's%20inclusion%20of%20regional%20partners%20in%20fostering%20people-to-people%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slew%20of%20announcements%20made%20at%20this%20year's%20Quad%20summit%2C%20and%20the%20resultant%20Wilmington%20Declaration%2C%20underscore%20the%20enduring%20promise%20and%20relevance%20of%20the%20grouping.%20While%20Quad%20continues%20to%20respond%20to%20critical%20geopolitical%20challenges%20in%20the%20world%20-%20specifically%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20-%20it%20has%20also%20demonstrated%20a%20robust%20positive%20agenda%20to%20harness%20shared%20opportunities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20the%20Quad%20is%20here%20to%20stay%2C%20in%20pursuit%20of%20a%20free%20and%20open%20Indo-Pacific%20-%20one%20that%20is%20inclusive%20and%20resilient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Harsh%20V%20Pant%20is%20Vice%20President%20for%20Studies%20at%20ORF.%20Sayantan%20Haldar%20works%20with%20the%20Maritime%20Initiative%20at%20ORF)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727084880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F33b0679o_esfsr_625x300_22_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbiggest-takeaway-from-quad-summit-is-that-its-here-to-stay-6630288%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20enduring%20wars%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20China's%20belligerent%20activities%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%20and%20emerging%20non-traditional%20security%20challenges%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20Quad%20had%20its%20task%20cut%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbiggest-takeaway-from-quad-summit-is-that-its-here-to-stay-6630288%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Cop%20Went%20To%20Solve%20Dispute%2C%20Was%20Shot%20In%20Face%20With%20Arrow%20In%20Bihar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20arrow%20pieced%20into%20the%20skull%20of%20a%20woman%20cop%20when%20a%20police%20team%20came%20under%20attack%20in%20Bihar's%20Araria%20on%20Monday.%20The%20police%20team%20had%20reached%20Jokihat%20to%20resolve%20a%20land%20dispute%20when%20they%20were%20attacked%20using%20bow%20and%20arrows.%20The%20woman%20cop%20was%20hit%20in%20her%20face%20with%20the%20arrow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cop%20has%20been%20admitted%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Purnea.%20She%20is%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20details%20are%20awaited.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727084760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fhhdd2qpg_cop-hit-by-arrow_625x300_23_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fwoman-cop-went-to-solve-dispute-was-shot-in-face-with-arrow-in-bihar-6630228%22%2C%22summary%22%3