cebook%2C%20that%20promised%20to%20show%20parents%20how%20to%20find%20college%20scholarships.%20The%20free%20introductory%20video%20for%20the%20course%20recommended%20using%20a%20combination%20of%20search%20terms%2C%20like%20%26quot%3Bscholarship%20AND%20North%20Carolina%20AND%20community%20service.%26quot%3B%20Siobhan%20felt%20like%20she%20had%20cracked%20the%20code.%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20God%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Maggie.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20it.%26quot%3B%20The%20scholarships%20were%20out%20there%3B%20they%20just%20needed%20to%20look%20for%20them%20in%20the%20right%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20this%20new%20knowledge%2C%20Siobhan%20and%20Maggie%20attacked%20the%20scholarship%20problem%20with%20renewed%20vigor.%20They%20applied%20for%20close%20to%20100%20scholarships.%20But%20in%20the%20end%2C%20nothing%20happened.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20get%20any%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Maggie%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BI%20mean%20as%20far%20as%20I%20know%2C%20since%20I%20didn't%20hear%20anything%20from%20them.%20It%20was%20a%20complete%20waste%20of%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20students%20like%20Maggie%20devote%20countless%20hours%20to%20the%20hunt%20for%20private%20scholarships%20to%20pay%20for%20college.%20And%20like%20her%2C%20most%20end%20up%20with%20nothing%20to%20show%20for%20their%20efforts.%20Mark%20Kantrowitz%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20student%20financial%20aid%2C%20analyzed%20federal%20data%20and%20concluded%20that%20in%20the%202019%20school%20year%2C%20only%2015%25%20of%20college%20students%20received%20a%20private%20grant%20or%20scholarship.%20And%20the%20lucky%20few%20who%20hit%20the%20private-aid%20jackpot%20didn't%20come%20away%20with%20much%20in%20the%20way%20of%20winnings.%20The%20average%20scholarship%2C%20Kantrowitz%20found%2C%20was%20under%20%245%2C000.%20And%2097%25%20of%20recipients%20received%20%242%2C500%20or%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-tuition-costs-too-much-make-degrees-matter-less-jobs-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20cost%20of%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20relatively%20low%20levels%20of%20aid%20available%20to%20students%2C%20has%20not%20only%20created%20a%20crisis%20of%20affordability%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20also%20given%20birth%20to%20an%20entire%20industry%20that%20dangles%20money%20in%20front%20of%20desperate%20families.%20Private%20scholarships%20have%20been%20around%20for%20decades%2C%20but%20in%20olden%20times%20students%20had%20to%20go%20to%20a%20public%20library%20or%20the%20school%20counseling%20office%20to%20look%20through%20a%20giant%20book%20of%20grants.%20The%20modern%20search%20industry%20was%20created%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20when%20the%20internet%20made%20it%20infinitely%20easier%20for%20students%20everywhere%20to%20grab%20information%20from%20anywhere.%20Fastweb%2C%20for%20example%2C%20began%20as%20a%20relatively%20small%20company%20in%201995%2C%20but%20in%202001%20it%20was%20bought%20by%20the%20job-search%20site%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chicagotribune.com%2F2001%2F07%2F19%2Ffastwebs-style-not-rock-n-roll-but-its-working%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fmonster.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonster.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chicagotribune.com%2F2001%2F07%2F19%2Ffastwebs-style-not-rock-n-roll-but-its-working%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E's%20parent%20company%20for%20%2460%20million%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20see%20what%20students%20are%20dealing%20with%2C%20I%20took%20a%20look%20at%20Fastweb%2C%20which%20bills%20itself%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20leading%20scholarship%20database%26quot%3B%20designed%20to%20simplify%20the%20scholarship%20search.%20%26quot%3BNo%20more%20digging%20to%20find%20scholarships%20you%20qualify%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company's%20website%20promises.%20%26quot%3BStudents%20create%20a%20profile%20and%20get%20personalized%20scholarship%20recommendations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20I%20could%20see%20what%20Fastweb%20had%20to%20offer%2C%20I%20was%20required%20to%20create%20an%20account%20with%20my%20birthdate%2C%20gender%2C%20and%20contact%20information.%20That%2C%20experts%20say%2C%20is%20how%20scholarship%20sites%20make%20money%20from%20the%20supposedly%20%26quot%3Bfree%26quot%3B%20services%20they%20provide.%20%26quot%3BThe%20primary%20reason%20these%20sites%20exist%20is%20to%20gather%20data%20from%20students%20and%20sell%20names%20to%20other%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeff%20Levy%2C%20an%20independent%20education%20consultant%2C%20told%20me.%20Sure%20enough%2C%20before%20I%20was%20allowed%20to%20begin%20my%20search%2C%20Fastweb%20invited%20me%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20several%20newsletters%2C%20download%20its%20app%2C%20fill%20out%20a%20more%20complete%20personal%20profile%2C%20and%20agree%20to%20share%20my%20info%20with%20colleges%20so%20they%20could%20reach%20out%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20declining%20all%20the%20offers%2C%20I%20finally%20got%20to%20see%20my%20%26quot%3Bpersonalized%26quot%3B%20list.%20Great%20news!%20There%20were%2057%20scholarships%20worth%20a%20grand%20total%20of%20%2410.3%20million%20waiting%20for%20me%20to%20apply!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20list%2C%20though%2C%20things%20got%20a%20lot%20less%20exciting.%20Almost%20all%20of%20that%20ridiculous%20total%20came%20from%20an%20invitation%20to%20enter%20the%20%2410%20million%20Publisher's%20Clearing%20House%20sweepstakes.%20No%20word%20on%20whether%20you'd%20get%20your%20scholarship%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20giant%20check%20delivered%20by%20the%20ghost%20of%20Ed%20McMahon.%20The%20next%20largest%20scholarship%20offered%20me%20%24100%2C000%20to%20%3Cem%3Eskip%3C%2Fem%3E%20college.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-thiel-fellow-program-skip-woke-college-education-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo-year%20%26quot%3Bfellowship%26quot%3B%20was%20from%20the%20Thiel%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20named%20after%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20billionaire%20Peter%20Thiel%2C%20for%20students%20%26quot%3Bwho%20want%20to%20build%20new%20things%20instead%20of%20sitting%20in%20a%20classroom.%26quot%3B%20No%20word%20on%20whether%20you'd%20get%20your%20scholarship%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20giant%20check%20delivered%20by%20an%20AI%20bot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20of%20the%20scholarships%20appeared%20to%20employ%20lottery%20drawings%20rather%20than%20merit-based%20competitions.%20One%20of%20the%20largest%20offered%20a%20%2425%2C000%20%26quot%3BNo%20Essay%26quot%3B%20scholarship%2C%20awarded%20each%20year%20by%20Niche%2C%20an%20educational-ranking%20website.%20It%20was%20hard%20not%20to%20interpret%20that%20offer%20as%20a%20way%20to%20lure%20students%20off%20Fastweb's%20site%20and%20onto%20another.%20After%20those%20jumbo%20prizes%2C%20the%20jackpots%20got%20much%20smaller.%20The%20majority%20were%20for%20%242%2C500%20or%20less.%20One%20was%20worth%20%2425.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20irony%20is%20kind%20of%20thick%2C%20and%20a%20bit%20sad%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ron%20Lieber%2C%20a%20personal%20finance%20expert%20who%20teaches%20an%20online%20course%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fmeritaidcourse.com%2F%26source%3Dgmail-imap%26ust%3D1725467389000000%26usg%3DAOvVaw0zltwUZBNDNTzBOrexTJcP%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20get%20merit%20scholarships%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20sites%20often%20aren't%20of%20much%20help%20to%20students%2C%20he%20told%20me%2C%20yet%20they%20profit%20by%20selling%20the%20student%20data%20they%20collect%20to%20colleges.%20%26quot%3BKids%20think%20they're%20going%20to%20get%20money%2C%20while%20schools%20that%20already%20cannot%20meet%20their%20full%20financial%20need%20pay%20money%20for%20access%20to%20those%20kids%2C%20to%20peddle%20educations%20that%20might%20not%20be%20affordable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20hey%2C%20every%20little%20bit%20helps%2C%20right%3F%20Maybe%20not%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20phenomenon%20known%20as%20scholarship%20displacement.%20When%20a%20student%20wins%20an%20outside%20scholarship%2C%20many%20colleges%20respond%20by%20reducing%20the%20financial%20aid%20they%20provide%20the%20student.%20If%20a%20student%20receives%20a%20%242%2C000%20scholarship%20from%20their%20local%20Rotary%20club%2C%20say%2C%20the%20college%20simply%20slashes%20its%20institutional%20aid%20to%20the%20student%20by%20that%20amount.%20In%20effect%2C%20they%20pocket%20the%20scholarship%20the%20student%20worked%20so%20hard%20to%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20difficult%20to%20know%20how%20many%20colleges%20displace%20private%20scholarships%2C%20or%20how%20many%20students%20are%20affected%20by%20it.%20In%202013%2C%20a%20small%20study%20conducted%20by%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20Community%20Foundation%20found%20that%20one%20in%20five%20colleges%20engaged%20in%20the%20practice.%20Since%20then%2C%20advocates%20believe%2C%20the%20number%20has%20likely%20gone%20down%2C%20thanks%20to%20bans%20on%20scholarship%20displacement%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcalmatters.org%2Feducation%2Fhigher-education%2Fcollege-beat%2F2022%2F11%2Fscholarship-displacement-california%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20California%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20when%20students%20are%20allowed%20to%20keep%20the%20money%2C%20they%20still%20get%20little%20help%20from%20private%20scholarships.%20To%20see%20how%20much%20outside%20grants%20contribute%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffafsa-how-to-get-college-financial-aid-chaotic-rollout-delays-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20aid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20analyzed%201%2C400%20schools%20that%20report%20the%20dollar%20value%20of%20all%20grants.%20On%20average%2C%20I%20found%2C%20private%20scholarships%20account%20for%20only%205%25%20of%20the%20aid%20going%20to%20students.%20At%20half%20the%20schools%2C%20it%20was%203%25%20or%20less.%20Even%20if%20you're%20lucky%20enough%20to%20win%20an%20outside%20scholarship%2C%20the%20payoff%20won't%20make%20much%20of%20a%20dent%20in%20your%20college%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%2C%20it's%20a%20black%20hole%20that%20can%20waste%20a%20bunch%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dawn%20Brady%2C%20a%20mother%20in%20San%20Diego%20whose%20son%20tried%20to%20find%20money%20on%20one%20of%20the%20scholarship%20sites%20to%20help%20pay%20for%20his%20freshman%20year%20at%20Lehigh%20University.%20%26quot%3BGetting%20a%20job%20and%20saving%20money%20would%20be%20a%20better%20way%20to%20spend%20your%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20small%20aid%20and%20low%20chances%20of%20success%2C%20none%20of%20the%20experts%20I%20spoke%20to%20tell%20students%20not%20to%20bother%20looking%20for%20private%20scholarships.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20hard%20argument%20to%20tell%20students%20not%20to%20apply%20for%20scholarships%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chris%20Reeves%2C%20a%20college%20admissions%20consultant.%20%26quot%3BBut%20most%20of%20the%20money%20is%20going%20to%20come%20from%20colleges.%26quot%3B%20Aisosa%20Ede-Osifo%2C%20a%20public%20school%20counselor%20in%20Dallas%2C%20gives%20students%20a%20similar%20message.%20Given%20the%20small%20sums%20at%20stake%2C%20she%20tells%20them%2C%20the%20scholarship%20hunt%20%26quot%3Bmay%20not%20be%20the%20most%20efficient%20use%20of%20your%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20are%20cash-strapped%20families%20to%20do%3F%20For%20starters%2C%20consultants%20say%2C%20spend%20less%20time%20searching%20for%20private%20scholarships%20and%20more%20on%20the%20single%20biggest%20thing%20they%20can%20do%20to%20reduce%20the%20cost%20of%20college%3A%20applying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolleges-pay-best-for-their-cost-return-on-investment-roi-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschools%20that%20will%20be%20affordable%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20What%20matters%20most%20is%20the%20total%20cost%20of%20attendance%2C%20and%20how%20much%20the%20school%20provides%20in%20institutional%20aid.%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20you%20can%20get%20some%20outside%20scholarships%2C%26quot%3B%20Levy%20tells%20students.%20%26quot%3BBut%20you%20are%20stepping%20over%20dollars%20to%20pick%20up%20a%20nickel.%26quot%3B%20He%20encourages%20families%20to%20focus%20their%20time%20and%20energy%20on%20building%20a%20list%20of%20colleges%20that%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20award%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20aid%20to%20attract%20students%20who%20fit%20their%20institution's%20profile%20and%20priorities.%20Building%20this%20kind%20of%20list%20is%20not%20easy%2C%20Levy%20acknowledges%2C%20which%20is%20why%20he%20publishes%20an%20annual%20chart%20of%20the%20merit%20aid%20provided%20by%20some%20500%20colleges.%20To%20find%20a%20good%20financial%20fit%2C%20students%20can%20also%20consult%20the%20Department%20of%20Education's%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcollegescorecard.ed.gov%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20College%20Scorecard%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20lists%20the%20actual%20price%20families%20pay%20by%20income%20bracket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFocusing%20on%20institutional%20aid%20is%20what%20ultimately%20helped%20Maggie%20Beam.%20Once%20she%20got%20her%20financial%20aid%20offer%20from%20Winthrop%2C%20she%20told%20me%2C%20she%20gave%20up%20on%20outside%20scholarships%20and%20focused%20her%20considerable%20determination%20on%20getting%20more%20aid%20from%20the%20college.%20She%20called%20the%20school%20and%20submitted%20an%20appeal%20for%20more%20aid%2C%20which%20led%20to%20another%20%241%2C000.%20And%20after%20she%20and%20her%20mother%20went%20to%20campus%20and%20shared%20her%20final%20grades%20with%20the%20school's%20financial%20aid%20officers%2C%20she%20was%20awarded%20another%20%242%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20Maggie%20also%20benefited%20from%20taking%20a%20more%20strategic%20approach%20to%20her%20scholarship%20hunt.%20Rather%20than%20relying%20on%20websites%2C%20experts%20say%2C%20students%20should%20reach%20out%20to%20their%20high%20school%20counselor%20and%20others%20in%20their%20community.%20%26quot%3BStart%20where%20you%20have%20the%20least%20competition%2C%26quot%3B%20Charlain%20Bailey%2C%20a%20former%20guidance%20counselor%20who%20advises%20private%20clients%2C%20tells%20families.%20%26quot%3BStart%20within%20your%20circle.%26quot%3B%20The%20people%20who%20know%20you%20well%20are%20much%20more%20likely%20to%20connect%20you%20to%20an%20appropriate%20scholarship%20than%20a%20random%20search%20engine.%20And%20fewer%20students%20are%20vying%20for%20the%20local%20grants%2C%20which%20are%20often%20offered%20by%20churches%20and%20civic%20groups%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20what%20happened%20to%20Maggie.%20In%20her%20senior%20year%2C%20she%20got%20involved%20with%20a%20local%20organization%20called%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rightmovesforyouth.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Right%20Moves%20for%20Youth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20provides%20free%20mentoring%20and%20other%20support%20to%20public%20school%20students.%20In%20the%20spring%2C%20after%20Maggie%20had%20given%20up%20on%20the%20scholarship%20hunt%2C%20a%20mentor%20at%20Right%20Moves%20told%20her%20she%20should%20apply%20for%20a%20scholarship%20from%20the%20Schug%20Foundation%2C%20which%20awards%20grants%20of%20up%20to%20%245%2C000%20each%20year%20to%20100%20students%20from%20three%20counties%20in%20North%20Carolina.%20Maggie%20filled%20out%20the%20application%20and%20interviewed%20with%20the%20foundation's%20directors%2C%20who%20were%20impressed%20with%20her%20commitment%20to%20public%20service.%20In%20July%2C%20she%20found%20out%20she'd%20be%20getting%20an%20annual%20scholarship%20of%20%244%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20renewable%20for%20four%20years.%20Without%20the%20suggestion%20from%20the%20mentor%2C%20she%20told%20me%2C%20she%20wouldn't%20have%20known%20about%20the%20foundation.%20She%20got%20lucky%20inside%20her%20circle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAid%20advocates%20are%20trying%20to%20help%20other%2C%20less%20fortunate%20students%20get%20equally%20lucky.%20In%20an%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.commonapp.org%2Ffiles%2FCommon-App-partnerships-and-scholarship-awarding.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20ongoing%20pilot%20program%20at%20the%20Common%20Application%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20used%20by%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20colleges%20and%20a%20million%20students%2C%20applicants%20were%20invited%20to%20apply%20for%20one%20of%20200%20scholarships%20offered%20by%20the%20Equitable%20Foundation%20for%20low-income%20students%20of%20color%20who%20would%20be%20the%20first%20in%20their%20family%20to%20attend%20to%20college.%20The%20first%20year%20of%20the%20pilot%20was%20disappointing.%20Common%20App%20emailed%2035%2C000%20students%2C%20but%20only%20316%20applied%20for%20the%20scholarship%20and%20just%20two%20received%20an%20award.%20The%20following%20year%2C%20after%20getting%20Equitable%20to%20place%20greater%20emphasis%20on%20students%20with%20financial%20need%2C%20the%20number%20of%20award%20winners%20increased%20to%2040.%20And%20last%20year%2C%20after%20Common%20App%20began%20contacting%20eligible%20students%20within%20the%20portal%20itself%20and%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20grant%20providers%2C%20the%20total%20value%20of%20private%20scholarships%20students%20received%20soared%20from%20%24350%2C000%20in%202022%20to%20%244.8%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20combination%20of%20institutional%20aid%20and%20private%20scholarship%20she%20received%2C%20Maggie%20managed%20to%20cut%20her%20original%20college%20bill%20from%20%2415%2C000%20to%20%248%2C000.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20meant%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20mother%20told%20me%20%E2%80%94%20an%20assessment%20that%20downplays%20the%20perseverance%20and%20luck%20it%20required.%20But%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20the%20family's%20fortunes%20took%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse%3A%20Siobhan%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer.%20The%20illness%20is%20treatable%2C%20but%20it's%20likely%20to%20cost%20the%20family%20%245%2C000%20out%20of%20pocket%20%E2%80%94%20effectively%20wiping%20out%20the%20financial%20value%20of%20the%20private%20scholarship%20Maggie%20received.%20Even%20after%20their%20relatively%20rare%20success%20in%20scholarship%20hunting%2C%20Siobhan%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20pay%20Maggie's%20first-semester%20bill%20with%20a%20credit%20card.%20For%20far%20too%20many%20families%2C%20the%20hunt%20for%20affordability%20never%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjames-murphy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EJames%20S.%20Murphy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20higher%20education%20policy%20analyst%20at%20Education%20Reform%20Now.%20Follow%20him%20on%20Twitter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJames_S_Murphy%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Egoogle%257Ctwcamp%255Eserp%257Ctwgr%255Eauthor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E%40James_S_Murphy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-college-scholarship-waste-of-time-trap-strategies-financial-aid-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727083742000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ce2c461aa2ac29ee34bf74%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-college-scholarship-waste-of-time-trap-strategies-financial-aid-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Private%20college%20scholarships%20are%20hard%20to%20find%2C%20don't%20pay%20much%2C%20and%20often%20get%20deducted%20from%20other%20financial%20a