he%20victim%20filed%20a%20complaint%20at%20the%20Cyber%20Crime%20police%20station.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fhow-a-top-ludhiana-industrialist-lost-rs-1-crore-to-call-claiming-to-be-from-igi-airport-official%2Farticleshow%2F113595667.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Stranded'%20Sunita%20Williams%20Now%20Commands%20International%20Space%20Station%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian-origin%20NASA%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%20is%20now%20commander%20of%20the%20International%20Space%20Station.%20She%20was%20in%20space%20on%20an%20eight-day%20mission%20that%20had%20to%20be%20extended%20to%20over%20eight%20months%20because%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20spacecraft%20she%20travelled%20in%20faced%20technical%20glitches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20has%20announced%20that%20Russian%20cosmonaut%20Oleg%20Kononenko%20handed%20over%20the%20command%20of%20the%20space%20station%20to%20Sunita%20Williams%20at%20a%20ceremony%20onboard%20the%20space%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKononenko%20is%20completing%20a%20year-long%20mission%20on%20the%20station%20and%20is%20among%20three%20astronauts%2C%20along%20with%20Tracy%20C%20Dyson%20and%20Nikolai%20Chub%2C%20who%20are%20set%20to%20return%20to%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilliams%20has%20been%20working%20aboard%20the%20microgravity%20laboratory%20to%20advance%20scientific%20knowledge%20and%20demonstrate%20new%20technologies%20for%20future%20human%20and%20robotic%20exploration%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20time%20Sunita%20Williams%20is%20taking%20command%20of%20the%20ISS.%20She%20last%20took%20charge%2012%20years%20back.%20As%20commander%20of%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20her%20key%20responsibility%20will%20be%20to%20maintain%20safety%20onboard%20the%20space%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20formal%20handover%20event%2C%20Sunita%20Williams%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20Expedition%2071%20has%20taught%20all%20of%20us%20a%20lot%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20adapt%2C%20you%20adopted%20Butch%20and%20me%20even%20though%20that%20was%20not%20part%20of%20the%20plan%2C%20you%20welcomed%20us%20as%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOleg%20Kononenko%20formally%20handed%20over%20a%20golden%20key%20to%20Sunita%20Williams%20--%20a%20part%20used%20in%20the%20Soyuz%20spacecraft's%20docking%20port.%20An%20elated%20Sunita%20Williams%20was%20seen%20swirling%20and%20playing%20with%20the%20key%20in%20the%20near%20zero%20gravity%20environment%20of%20the%20ISS.%20In%20all%2C%20she%20has%20spent%20431%20days%20in%20space%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20return%20to%20Earth%20on%20the%20SpaceX%20Crew%20Dragon%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Sunita%20Williams%20shared%20her%20thoughts%20on%20the%20unexpected%20delay%20and%20described%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20as%20her%20%26quot%3Bhappy%20place%26quot%3B.%20She%20mentioned%20how%20life%20in%20space%20has%20not%20been%20a%20difficult%20adjustment%20due%20to%20her%20previous%20experience%20--%20this%20is%20her%20third%20sojourn%20into%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Space%20Station%20is%20like%20a%20mini-city%20in%20space%20that%20has%20been%20flying%20for%2025%20years.%20The%20ISS%20weighs%20419%20tonnes%2C%20and%20costs%20over%20%24150%20billion.%20It%20is%20the%20size%20of%20a%20football%20field%20--%20about%20109%20metres%20long.%20Astronauts%20see%2016%20sunrises%20daily%20in%20its%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%206%2C%20after%20she%20reached%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20Sunita%20Williams%20hugged%20the%20crew%20members.%20%26quot%3BA%20big%20thanks%20to%20family%20and%20friends%20who%20lived%20this%20%5Bmoment%5D%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20I%20think%20you%20are%20glad%20we%20are%20not%20with%20you%20anymore%20and%20we%20have%20another%20family%20up%20here%20which%20is%20just%20awesome%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20to%20Dr%20Deepak%20Pandya%20and%20Bonnie%20Pandya%2C%2059-year-old%20Sunita%20Williams%20is%20also%20a%20Navy-trained%20pilot.%20She%20is%20also%20a%20marathon%20runner%20and%20ran%20one%20while%20on%20the%20International%20Space%20Station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lover%20of%20Indian%20cuisine%2C%20Sunita%20Williams%20will%20have%20fish%20curry%20during%20her%20space%20flight%2C%20NASA%20has%20confirmed.%20During%20her%20earlier%20flights%2C%20she%20has%20enjoyed%20samosas%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20her%20flight%2C%20Sunita%20Williams%20had%20told%20NDTV%20that%20she%20would%20carry%20an%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Ganesh%20with%20her%20as%20it%20was%20her%20good%20luck%20charm.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727083620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fhpp478o8_sunita-williams_625x300_23_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fstranded-sunita-williams-now-commands-international-space-station-6630143%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian-origin%20NASA%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%20is%20now%20commander%20of%20the%20International%20Space%20Station.%20She%20was%20in%20space%20on%20an%20eight-day%20mission%20that%20had%20to%20be%20extended%20to%20over%20eight%20months%20because%20the%20spacecraft%20she%20travelled%20in%20faced%20glitches%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fstranded-sunita-williams-now-commands-international-space-station-6630143%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210%20greatest%20women%20scientists%20%26amp%3B%20their%20significant%20contributions%20in%20science%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727083556000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113595534%2Cimgsize-49854.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%