in%20divinity%20and%20spirituality.%20Then%20only%20will%20our%20children%20get%20the%20inner%20strength%2C%20it%20will%20help%20in%20their%20progress%20and%20that%20of%20the%20country.%20That%20is%20my%20strong%20belief%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20sparked%20a%20row%2C%20with%20social%20media%20users%20accusing%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20of%20making%20insensitive%20remarks%20without%20addressing%20the%20issue%20of%20toxic%20workplaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriyanka%20Chaturvedi%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%2C%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Finance%20Minister's%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDear%20Nirmala%20Sitaraman%20ji%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnna%20had%20inner%20strength%20to%20handle%20the%20stress%20that%20came%20with%20pursuing%20a%20gruelling%20Chartered%20Accountancy%20degree.%20It%20was%20the%20toxic%20work%20culture%2C%20long%20work%20hours%20that%20took%20away%20her%20life%20which%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed.%20Stop%20victim%20shaming%20and%20atleast%20try%20to%20be%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHP9vMrX3qR%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FHP9vMrX3qR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20(%40priyankac19)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpriyankac19%2Fstatus%2F1838065934759514160%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDear%20Nirmala%20Sitaraman%20ji%2C%20Anna%20had%20(the)%20inner%20strength%20to%20handle%20the%20stress%20that%20came%20with%20pursuing%20a%20gruelling%20Chartered%20Accountancy%20degree.%20It%20was%20the%20toxic%20work%20culture%2C%20long%20work%20hours%20that%20took%20away%20her%20life%20which%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed.%20Stop%20victim%20shaming%20and%20at%20least%20try%20to%20be%20a%20little%20sensitive%2C%20am%20sure%20god%20will%20be%20the%20guide%20if%20you%20seek.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECPI%20MP%20P%20Sandosh%20Kumar%20accused%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20of%20%26quot%3Bbelittling%20and%20demeaning%20everyday%20struggles%20of%20working%20people%20across%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BOver-work%2C%20inhuman%20working%20conditions%2C%20pervasive%20unemployment%20and%20lack%20of%20social%20security%20are%20creating%20stress%20and%20insecurity%20among%20workers%2C%20particularly%20the%20younger%20sections%20of%20our%20workforce%20across%20occupations.%20Instead%20of%20addressing%20these%20structural%20concerns%2C%20the%20finance%20minister's%20advice%20to%20'rely%20on%20God'%20is%20bizarre%20and%20insensitive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20Opposition%20leaders%2C%20several%20social%20media%20users%20found%20the%20remarks%20insensitive%20and%20said%20the%20government%20should%20address%20the%20toxic%20work%20culture%20in%20many%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnna%20Sebastian%20Perayil's%20death%20has%20sparked%20a%20nationwide%20conversation%20on%20how%20toxic%20workplaces%20are%20affecting%20the%20well-being%20of%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20came%20to%20light%20after%20Anna's%20mother%20Anita%20Augustine%20wrote%20to%20Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20India%20Chairman%20Rajiv%20Memani%20and%20said%20her%20daughter%20had%20died%20just%20four%20months%20after%20she%20joined%20the%20company%20and%20flagged%20a%20work%20culture%20that%20%26quot%3Bseems%20to%20glorify%20overwork%20while%20neglecting%20the%20very%20human%20being%20behind%20the%20role%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnna%20would%20return%20to%20her%20room%20utterly%20exhausted%2C%20sometimes%20collapsing%20on%20the%20bed%20without%20even%20changing%20her%20clothes%2C%20only%20to%20be%20bombarded%20with%20messages%20asking%20for%20more%20reports.%20She%20was%20putting%20in%20her%20best%20efforts%2C%20working%20very%20hard%20to%20meet%20the%20deadlines.%20She%20was%20a%20fighter%20to%20the%20core%2C%20not%20someone%20to%20give%20up%20easily.%20We%20told%20her%20to%20quit%2C%20but%20she%20wanted%20to%20learn%20and%20gain%20new%20exposure.%20However%2C%20the%20overwhelming%20pressure%20proved%20too%20much%20even%20for%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EErnst%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20India%20has%20said%20it%20was%20deeply%20saddened%20by%20Anna's%20death%20and%20was%20taking%20the%20family's%20correspondence%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Butmost%20seriousness%20and%20humility%26quot%3B.%20In%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20Mr%20Memani%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20deeply%20saddened%20and%20as%20a%20father%2C%20I%20can%20only%20imagine%20Ms%20Augustine's%20grief.%20I%20have%20conveyed%20my%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20the%20family%2C%20although%20nothing%20can%20fill%20the%20void%20in%20their%20lives.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20affirm%20that%20the%20well-being%20of%20our%20people%20is%20my%20top-most%20priority%20and%20I%20will%20personally%20champion%20this%20objective.%20I%20am%20absolutely%20committed%20to%20nurturing%20a%20harmonious%20workplace%2C%20and%20I%20will%20not%20rest%20until%20that%20objective%20is%20accomplished.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Labour%20Ministry%20has%20now%20launched%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20allegations%20of%20an%20unsafe%20and%20exploitative%20work%20environment.%20%26quot%3BDeeply%20saddened%20by%20the%20tragic%20loss%20of%20Anna%20Sebastian%20Perayil.%20A%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20the%20allegations%20of%20an%20unsafe%20and%20exploitative%20work%20environment%20is%20underway.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20justice%20%26amp%3B%20%40LabourMinistry%20has%20officially%20taken%20up%20the%20complaint.%20%40mansukhmandviya%2C%26quot%3B%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Labour%20Shobha%20Karandlaje%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20