%20Goswami.%20The%20screenplay%20and%20dialogue%20are%20written%20by%20Sneha%20Desai%2C%20while%20Divyanidhi%20Sharma%20has%20taken%20care%20of%20the%20additional%20dialogues.%20Laapataa%20Ladies%20had%20a%20screening%20at%20the%20prestigious%20Toronto%20International%20Film%20Festival%20(TIFF)%20last%20year.%20The%20film%20was%20released%20in%20theatres%20in%20India%20on%20March%201.%20The%20film%20has%20been%20applauded%20by%20critics%20and%20audiences%20alike.%20Despite%20not%20minting%20a%20whopping%20amount%20of%20money%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20the%20film%20garnered%20a%20new%20fanbase%20after%20it%20was%20released%20on%20the%20streaming%20giant%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbrb-still-laughing-at-photoshop-of-laapataa-ladies-phool-at-met-gala-5610213%5C%22%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Kiran%20Rao%20shared%20a%20snippet%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20film%20on%20social%20media%20and%20she%20captioned%20it%2C%20%26quot%3BLaapataa%20Ladies%20will%20be%20found%20in%20Japan%20from%20October%204%2C%202024.%20We%20are%20so%20excited%20for%20our%20theatrical%20release%20in%20Japan%20by%20Shochiku%2C%20Japan%20-%20arigato%20gozaimasu.%26quot%3B%20The%20film%20is%20a%20take%20against%20the%20patriarchal%20shackles%20which%20tend%20to%20bind%20women's%20aspirations%20and%20dreams%20within%20the%20four%20walls%20of%20domesticity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Flaapataa-ladies-reviewed-by-fardeen-khan-absolutely-loved-this-film-5618399%5C%22%3EThe%20film%20opened%20to%20largely%20positive%20reviews%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20film%20critics.%20In%20his%20review%20for%20NDTV%2C%20film%20critic%20Saibal%20Chatterjee%20gave%20Laapataa%20Ladies%203.5%20stars%20out%20of%205%20and%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BAdapted%20from%20a%20story%20by%20Biplab%20Goswami%20and%20scripted%20by%20Sneha%20Desai%20(who%20has%20also%20written%20the%20dialogues%20with%20additional%20inputs%20from%20Divyanidhi%20Sharma)%2C%20Laapataa%20Ladies%20is%20a%20social%20satire%20with%20a%20pronounced%20feminist%20accent%20that%20gives%20the%20film%20its%20rationale.%20The%20film%20is%20breezy%20and%20light%20on%20its%20feet.%20It%20is%20never%2C%20therefore%2C%20in%20danger%20of%20being%20bogged%20down%20by%20the%20weighty%20issues%20that%20it%20addresses.%20Its%20simple%20clarion%20call%20is%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20women%20who%20are%20robbed%20of%20their%20dreams%20post-marriage%20and%20it%20is%20couched%20in%20simple%20methods%20that%20do%20not%20seek%20to%20draw%20too%20much%20attention%20to%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727078640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F8scfrgg_ladies-_625x300_23_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Flaapataa-ladies-is-indias-official-entry-for-oscars-2025-6629202%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Laapataa%20Ladies%20is%20directed%20by%20Kiran%20Rao%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Flaapataa-ladies-is-indias-official-entry-for-oscars-2025-6629202%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Officer%20Black%20Belt%20needs%20an%20edgier%20narrative%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727078608000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113592541%2Cimgsize-21992.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fofficer-black-belt-review-kim-woo-bins-action-avatar-and-simplistic-charm-deserve-an-edgier-narrative%2Farticleshow%2F113592430.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113592430.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKim%20Woo%20Bin%20stars%20as%20Lee%20Jung-do%20in