rt%20baby%20girl%20foetuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20effects%20of%20the%20Bibipur%20model%20have%20trickled%20into%20Gurugram.%20As%20Ramchander%2C%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20Makhrola%20village%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20model%20of%20village%20development%20was%20introduced%20in%20our%20village%20a%20year%20ago.%20While%20on%20paper%2C%20women%20had%20an%20equal%20participation%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359001%2Fias-officer-balika-panchayat-nanded-maharashtra-young-girls-fight-alcoholism-child-marriage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Epanchayat%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecommittees%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20reality%20was%20very%20different.%20Their%20husbands%20would%20be%20attending%20in%20place%20of%20them.%20But%20now%2C%20women%20are%20not%20only%20called%20for%20assemblies%2C%20they%20actively%20participate%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Epanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Jaglan%20spoke%20to%20women%20about%20their%20concerns%20regarding%20female%20foeticide%2C%20dowry%2C%20harassment%20and%20domestic%20violence%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327-150x79