rban%20settlement%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Leh%20town%2C%20Dr%20Lobzang%20Chorol%20witnessed%20firsthand%20the%20critical%20role%20water%20plays%20in%20this%20cold%20desert.%20Speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Dr%20Chorol%20recalls%20two%20specific%20incidents%20that%20left%20an%20indelible%20impression%20on%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20childhood%2C%20I%20vividly%20remember%20a%20summer%20when%20the%20PHE%20(Public%20Health%20and%20Engineering)%20tanker%20failed%20to%20arrive%2C%20leaving%20us%20without%20a%20water%20supply.%20We%20had%20to%20walk%20long%20distances%20to%20fetch%20water%20for%20our%20basic%20needs.%20I%20saw%20the%20worry%20on%20my%20parent%E2%80%99s%20faces%20and%20the%20strain%20it%20put%20on%20our%20entire%20community.%20This%20crisis%20opened%20my%20eyes%20to%20the%20fragility%20of%20our%20water%20resources%20and%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20better%20management%20and%20understanding%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20incident%20Dr%20Chorol%20recalls%20is%20from%20her%20undergraduate%20days%20when%20she%20visited%20her%20ancestral%20village%20called%20Skumpata%20(Lingshet)%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F302635%2Fladakh-ministry-of-education-score-new-heights-role-of-dedicated-teachers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELadakh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20about%2080%20km%20from%20Leh%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20struck%20by%20the%20ingenious%20traditional%20water%20management%20systems%20our%20ancestors%20had%20developed%20%E2%80%94%20the%20intricate%20network%20of%20channels%20and%20storage%20ponds%20that%20had%20sustained%20life%20in%20this%20harsh%20landscape%20for%20centuries.%20However%2C%20I%20also%20noticed%20how%20these%20systems%20were%20under%20threat%20from%20changing%20climate%20patterns%20and%20modernisation.%20It%20made%20me%20realise%20the%20i