kh.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20temperature%20recorded%20in%20the%20Kargil%20division%20was%2037.5%C2%B0C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELadakh%20was%20burning%20this%20summer%20because%20of%20a%20huge%20deficit%20in%20rainfall.%20It%20received%203%20mm%20of%20rainfall%20till%20the%20start%20of%20August%20as%20against%20the%20normal%20of%2015%20mm.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lack%20of%20precipitation%20and%20intense%20heat%20wave%20has%20dried%20out%20the%20soil%2C%20causing%20crops%20to%20wither%20and%20trees%20to%20require%20more%20water.%20Meanwhile%2C%20groundwater%20exploitation%20by%20drilling%20more%20borewells%20has%20further%20accelerated%20the%20decline%20in%20groundwater%20levels%20and%20reserves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20all%20know%2C%20Leh%20is%20located%20in%20a%20high-altitude%20desert%20region%2C%20where%20the%20primary%20source%20of%20water%20for%20our%20aquifers%20is%20the%20melting%20of%20glaciers%20and%20snowpack%20in%20the%20surrounding%20mountains.%20However%2C%20as%20recent%20events%20indicate%2C%20climate%20change%20is%20causing%20significant%20alterations%20to%20this%20delicate%20balance%2C%20leading%20to%20severe%20consequences%20for%20our%20groundwater%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-1726234110.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Overview%20of%20Leh%20Town%3A%20Climate%20change%20is%20wreaking%20havoc%20on%20the%20region's%20groundwater%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-1726234110.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-1726234110-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-1726234110-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.c